Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》 第二季{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一只丽龟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.02,0:00:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}正在哥斯达黎加的浅水区休息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它游了一千六百多公里才来到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是因为它必须要到陆地上去产卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.34,0:01:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它又回到了自己十年前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}孵化的沙滩上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.14,0:01:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它必须离开自己那安全的海洋世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.46,0:01:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}勇敢面对远方的陌生世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它身上载有很重的卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但它肩负的是丽龟的下一代的命运{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在沙滩沿岸 这一壮观景象数百万年来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一直未曾变过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}从海里浮出的丽龟妈妈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数以十万计{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.06,0:02:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有那些能够克服陆地和海洋上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}各种艰难险阻的动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}才能抵达这里的海岸 达成生命最重要的使命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.32,0:03:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海岸是个瞬息万变的地方 同时也有着丰厚报酬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}加拉帕格斯群岛位于热带太平洋上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的海岸草木不生 看似不宜居住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是岸上却有一群动物能将其为己所用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.26,0:04:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一群尚未交配的雄海狮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们需要快速增加体重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因为只有体格最大的雄海狮才能吸引雌海狮与其交配繁殖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果这些年轻海狮长得不够大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那它们就要在这偏僻的海岸线上继续流亡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一只饥饿的年轻海狮单独出发了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它要去寻找大型猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}黄鳍金枪鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一条黄鳍金枪鱼就重达60千克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.38,0:05:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的最高游速可达64千米每小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它没法在外海抓到黄鳍金枪鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是它有个计划{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}前方是一个小海湾的入口处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它把黄鳍金枪鱼往小海湾里赶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这群金枪鱼中了它的圈套{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们陷入了绝境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过最后它们还是逃走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狮的计划落空了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过也许还有其他办法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.30,0:07:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这次海狮是成群结伴地出发{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们要把更多的金枪鱼围起来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}再把它们逼进小海湾里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狮们成扇形排开 将金枪鱼朝着狭口逼进{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}金枪鱼又一次陷入了绝境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是这一次 那只年轻海狮往回游{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}像路障一样堵住了出口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一次 这群金枪鱼想要逃跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}却被海狮堵了回去 陷入了死胡同中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狮们这下可以挨个干掉它们了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这种捕鱼技术{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}需要的是深谋远虑 详密计划和合作精神{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只有在加拉帕格斯群岛 我们才能见识到这么高明的计策{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每只大鱼的蛋白质含量要比它们平时的猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}高五倍左右{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}最终这只年轻海狮离开了自己的岗位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}去认领自己的奖品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}以富含蛋白质的金枪鱼为食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.94,0:10:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它很快就会发育成体格健壮的育种海狮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在海岸两个世界相遇的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些加拉帕格斯群岛的海狮利用这个小海湾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}把握住了这里的机会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在所有的海洋栖息地里 海岸是变化最为迅速的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这是因为潮汐的缘故{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海水在月球引力的作用下发生涨落 就形成了潮汐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}月球在绕着地球旋转时 海水也会随之起伏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}通常每天会发生两次潮汐现象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海岸也成了地球上最充满变化的风景{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他地方的海洋生物都不用应对这样变化莫测的环境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每天都要在太阳底下暴晒 还冒着脱水的危险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}拍打岩岸的潮水退去时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}会留下一片临时绿洲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.90,0:12:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}岩池{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.82,0:12:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里看上去似乎是个平静的庇护所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这只是一时的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}快进观察这里的情况 就会看到意想不到的戏剧性画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在岩池里 食草动物 食腐动物和滤食性动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}必须要在涨潮之前尽量利用好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.02,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这短短的几个小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海葵碰到任何东西就会将其一口吞下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过有些食物却比其他食物更难消化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些神奇的世界很快就会变成战场{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只致命的捕食者长有五条腕 口部位于底面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它就是赭色海星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它现在在寻找帽贝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一些帽贝无处可逃 海星将它们吞噬了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是其他帽贝却暗藏着防身手段{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们使出了滑溜的护盾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样它们就可以溜走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.06,0:15:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只帽贝有自己的保镖{\r}
