Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是有一种动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}会让帽贝毫无招架之力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.66,0:16:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}喉盘鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的牙齿能够伸至帽贝壳底下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}像拧瓶盖一样将帽贝拧开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着喉盘鱼就将帽贝连壳带肉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.02,0:16:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一并吞下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在涨潮之前 岩池里的这类戏剧性场面{\r}
