Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这也带来了新的机遇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一只红石蟹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和其他数千只普通滨蟹一样 也在等待着时机{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们每天都聚集到巴西的热带海岸上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}等着潮水退去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这样它们的觅食区就露出来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}覆满海草的岩石距离海岸大约是100米{\r}
