Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们怕的是海鳝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}链蛇鳝可是捕蟹专家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.54,0:19:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的钝牙能轻易抓住蟹壳 并将其压碎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}链蛇鳝是螃蟹的天敌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过螃蟹的觅食地还在远方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们必须要抓紧时间赶路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在还剩下半程{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.38,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过它们的敌人却打着其他主意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们要穿过陆地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}重新进行伏击{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了觅食 螃蟹只能继续赶路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是没有一个地方是安全的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}章鱼同样也是螃蟹的天敌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.58,0:21:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}螃蟹们朝前猛冲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成功了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们冒着性命威胁和失去腿的危险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一心只想到海草场上啃食海草{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是两个小时后 潮水开始退去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.38,0:22:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们又得冒着性命危险 再经过那恐怖的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}对海岸产生影响的不单单是潮水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}远海区产生的巨浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}朝着海岸席卷而来 越靠近就变得越大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}浅海海床拖着巨浪下方{\r}
