Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着倒塌 破碎释放{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.82,0:23:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}世界上最大的可冲的海浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大多是在葡萄牙纳扎雷的海上形成{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每天 这沿岸边上的海浪冲击力相当于{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.94,0:23:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一百五十万吨的黄色炸药威力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}波浪的威力渐渐形成影响 改变了海岸的形状{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.30,0:24:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在欧洲某些地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海浪每年冲蚀的海岸线多达三米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.14,0:24:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海浪对岩石的冲蚀效果{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}往往要视石头的硬度而定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.98,0:24:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}软岩石的底部非常坚硬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.70,0:24:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}整个岩石形成了动人心魄的拱形结构{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.14,0:25:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海浪不断地冲击拍打{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.22,0:25:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}渐渐将岩石雕刻成了拱顶教堂形状{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.22,0:25:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就像西班牙北部这里的情况一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.02,0:25:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海浪的威力塑造了一座座高耸的堡垒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.74,0:25:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}比如北极地区的这些悬崖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.86,0:25:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}成了成千上万海鸟生育繁殖的栖息之地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.10,0:25:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些峭壁只能从空中进入{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.34,0:25:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}上面有很多缝隙和角落 抵达的动物可在里面栖息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.22,0:25:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是为了觅食 海鸟还得征服远处的海洋世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.14,0:26:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只海鹦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.14,0:26:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}既是渔夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.02,0:26:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}也是父亲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.66,0:26:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它有个终身伴侣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.94,0:26:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这对配偶要共同养育自己那数周大的海鹦宝宝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.06,0:26:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海鹦宝宝每天要吃五顿大餐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.74,0:26:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的父母只能轮流出去捉鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.02,0:26:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在轮到父亲去捉鱼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.18,0:27:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鱼群数量很少时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.50,0:27:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海鹦们必须要飞到48千米外的海上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.78,0:27:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}才能找到资源丰富的渔场{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.38,0:27:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一旦到达那里 它们就要扎进另一个世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.70,0:27:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鱼群丰富的地方很难找到 而且它们还会遇上其它捕鱼鸟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.62,0:27:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海雀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.26,0:28:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}和海鹦一样 海雀的翅膀也很短 而且同样擅长潜水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.94,0:28:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海鹦在水里屏住呼吸的时间能超过一分钟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.10,0:28:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而且能潜入水下40米的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.30,0:28:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}逮着一条鱼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.70,0:28:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过回家的路途还很遥远{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.86,0:28:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}疲惫不堪的海鹦在往返行程中已经飞了96千米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.50,0:28:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它马上要到家了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.94,0:29:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是这片海岸上却有海盗在守着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.82,0:29:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们就是短尾贼鸥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.50,0:29:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}能干的父亲母亲们在回程中遭到了抢劫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.14,0:30:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}短尾贼鸥那朝后倾斜的长翅膀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.14,0:30:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大大加强了它们的速度和灵活性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.74,0:30:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海鹦必须要选对时机{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.14,0:31:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}差一点就得逞了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.10,0:31:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海鹦在绝望中最后一次加速{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.58,0:31:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它总算逃离了险境{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.38,0:32:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}经过长达三小时的往返飞行后 海鹦终于安全到家了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.70,0:32:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的伴侣正在耐心地等着它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.62,0:32:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}今天它们的宝宝有饭吃了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.30,0:32:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是由于鱼群数量在减少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.18,0:32:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}很多海鹦发现 它们现在很难喂饱自己的孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.02,0:32:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如今海洋的情况处于不断变化当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.18,0:32:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海鹦要做称职的父母 只会难上加难{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.86,0:33:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}克服两个世界的种种挑战并不是件容易的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.02,0:33:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一种海洋生物差不多已经彻底放弃海洋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.54,0:33:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在一些遥远的太平洋岛屿上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.30,0:33:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}住着地球上陆生习性最为明显的鱼类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.70,0:33:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这个数米高的石灰岩悬崖上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.90,0:33:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一条八厘米长的鲇鱼选了个巢洞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.78,0:33:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在这上面它能够吃到大量海藻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.26,0:33:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而且也不用和海里的鱼类争夺食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.10,0:34:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}那些雌鱼就在它底下进食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.62,0:34:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它很想吸引雌鱼的注意力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.86,0:34:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是这些雌鱼都忙着做保湿工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.22,0:34:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让身体处于湿润状态非常重要 因为这些鱼要通过皮肤来呼吸{\r}
