Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.66,0:34:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}开始拍打自己的橙色鱼鳍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.06,0:34:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它引起了一条雌鱼的注意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.42,0:34:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这些太平洋鲇鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.34,0:34:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}似乎很怕海浪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.34,0:34:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的的水性很差{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.10,0:34:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在海中 它们很容易成为猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:35:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是时候再试一次了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.86,0:35:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌鱼动心了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.02,0:35:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是海浪又一次让它分了心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.18,0:35:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只雄鱼就是不肯放弃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.02,0:35:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雌鱼最终还是被它迷住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.26,0:35:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雄鱼让开了道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.38,0:36:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}让雌鱼进入它的洞穴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.18,0:36:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}雄鱼用自己性感的舞姿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.10,0:36:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}怂恿雌鱼在这里产卵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.02,0:36:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接着它就在洞穴里的安全位置给这些鱼卵受精{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.78,0:36:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲇鱼为了在陆地生活 放弃了海洋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.14,0:36:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他动物的做法更为成功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.10,0:36:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}只不过它们选择了不同的方向{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.70,0:37:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅放弃了飞行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.34,0:37:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}相反地 它们大多数时间都是在海里度过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.58,0:37:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅身上那细密的羽毛 俨然是一套光滑的救生服{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.94,0:37:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}非常适合这里冰冷的海水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.46,0:37:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是它们每年还是得上岸一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.46,0:37:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}南乔治亚岛 是一座靠近南极的荒凉岛屿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.82,0:37:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年春天 这里的海滩就成了地球上最繁忙的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:37:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}数以十万计的国王企鹅会回到这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.38,0:38:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们正在朝着集群走去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.22,0:38:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是行至中途 它们前面却挡着一堵地球上最大的海兽脂墙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.02,0:38:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}象海豹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.62,0:38:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在是繁殖期{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.78,0:38:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些四吨重的雄象海豹正在争夺眷群的控制权{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.66,0:38:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅还是最好等它们平静下来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.10,0:39:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它没法飞过这道屏障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.50,0:39:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它只能尽可能小心翼翼地走着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.98,0:39:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}希望这些睡着的庞然大物会继续躺着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.82,0:39:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小心点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.50,0:39:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接下来的情况可能会比较棘手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.94,0:40:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一只雄象海豹发起了挑战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.58,0:40:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅们可能会被卷入这种激烈的交锋当中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.70,0:40:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}八吨重的海豹脂撞到了一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.42,0:41:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只高大的海滩霸主获胜了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.02,0:41:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只企鹅从慌乱的场面中溜了过去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.34,0:41:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}前面是四万只幼企鹅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.50,0:41:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们既饥饿又兴奋得忘乎所以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.30,0:41:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但并不是所有企鹅都有幼企鹅要喂养{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.78,0:41:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这不都是它们来这里的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.74,0:42:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}而是出于其他原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.50,0:42:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这场考验耐力的测试是每只企鹅都必须经历的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.62,0:42:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}测试先从持续性瘙痒开始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.30,0:42:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因为数个月来都在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.90,0:42:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}波涛汹涌的南大洋里游泳 它的救生服已经被磨薄了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.34,0:42:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它采用了一种非常极端的解决办法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.18,0:42:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它要尽快把身上四层羽毛全都脱去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.98,0:42:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一过程也被称作是灾难性脱毛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.74,0:42:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在羽毛重新长出之前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.10,0:43:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅们会一直待在这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.26,0:43:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅们在饥饿中度过了一个月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.58,0:43:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在它们的防水御寒羽毛又一次长全了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.14,0:43:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅们消瘦又饥饿 迫不及待想要回到海里生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.34,0:44:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}得益于身上的防水羽毛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.78,0:44:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}企鹅们现在能够游刃有余地穿梭于两个世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.94,0:44:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}哪怕是地球上最严峻的环境 它们也能应对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.62,0:44:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}南乔治亚岛海岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.26,0:44:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}因为地处偏远 目前并没有遭到破坏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.62,0:44:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其他海岸线则要脆弱得多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.54,0:44:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些海岸线的变化速度比以往任何时候都要快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.74,0:45:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}地球上的主要城市有三分之二都是沿海城市{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.78,0:45:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}据估计 在未来十年内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.42,0:45:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在现今尚存的未开发海岸中 其中一成的海岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.02,0:45:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都会被人类开发利用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.22,0:45:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是每年佛罗里达州棕榈滩上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.06,0:45:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}都会出现一起壮观的事件 几乎没人注意到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.34,0:45:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}地球上规模最大的成群鲨鱼会聚集到沿海区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.70,0:45:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}蔷薇真鲨和黑边鳍真鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.46,0:45:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}共有一万头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.38,0:46:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每年一月 它们就会去寻找这类温暖的浅滩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.54,0:46:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}短暂停留后 它们就会继续朝北洄游{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.26,0:46:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}早在人类涉足这里以前 鲨鱼就聚集在这里了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.82,0:46:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是今天这些鲨鱼却面临着污染{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.54,0:46:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}栖地退化 过度捕捞等问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.62,0:46:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些问题是它们的祖先从未遭遇过的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.98,0:46:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}沿海生物现在不仅仅要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.26,0:46:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}征服自己的世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.78,0:47:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们还要面临很多人类带来的问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.70,0:47:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}幕后集锦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.02,0:47:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了拍摄非同寻常的沿海野生生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.94,0:47:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》第二季的团队{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.38,0:47:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}前往了地球上最遥远的几个海岸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.46,0:47:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中一个就是加拉帕格斯群岛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.06,0:47:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他们在这里求证一个令人难以置信的故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.54,0:47:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}故事是当地一位名为理查德伍拉科姆的摄影师讲述的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.06,0:47:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我当时在和我的一位朋友聊天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.74,0:47:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他是这里的渔夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.90,0:48:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他说有一天自己来到这里 来到这个海湾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.82,0:48:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}突然间 他看到一群海狮把这些大金枪鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.26,0:48:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}全赶到沙滩上了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.38,0:48:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我就想 挺有意思的 我才不信呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.38,0:48:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这听上去太不真实了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.54,0:48:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过渔夫的故事实在太诱人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.90,0:48:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他们没法置之不理{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.18,0:48:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我现在有点担心 这事要是不发生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.10,0:48:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我的信誉就毁了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.94,0:48:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}《蓝色星球》第二季的团队发起了全面的考察行动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.22,0:48:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过其中一位成员还是心存疑虑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.18,0:48:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果海狮真的能够追杀金枪鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.10,0:48:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一情景肯定很壮观{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.22,0:48:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过我觉得还是得眼见为实{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.82,0:48:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他们在这个荒芜的小海湾搭好了帐篷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.26,0:48:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}接下来几个月内他们就住在这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.58,0:48:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}当地的野生生物以温顺近人而闻名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.58,0:48:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们想见见自己的新邻居{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.14,0:49:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}由于没看到海狮的迹象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.58,0:49:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}考察团队就用远程水下摄像机监视情况{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.74,0:49:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}场地助理罗比佩普拉斯率先在这里守着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.18,0:49:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这个视角{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.82,0:49:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}是为了尽量让我们看到海狮游过来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.98,0:49:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}跃出水面的情形{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.74,0:49:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果它们真的游近了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.14,0:49:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}就会喊 “开拍”或者是“行动起来”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.46,0:49:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}三小时后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.54,0:49:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}瑞秋 我看到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.06,0:49:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}距离猎物还有150米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.86,0:49:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}空中摄制组率先出发了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.14,0:49:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一只海狮正在把金枪鱼赶往海湾里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.14,0:50:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}哦 它抓到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.82,0:50:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}太不可思议了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.34,0:50:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}瞧瞧 它还在挣扎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.50,0:50:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.30,0:50:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}金枪鱼跑了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.06,0:50:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}金枪鱼从海狮手里逃脱了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.14,0:50:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}在接下来的几天内 更多的海狮来到海湾里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.66,0:50:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}把黄鳍金枪鱼追进海湾里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.38,0:50:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.98,0:50:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}理查 这有更多金枪鱼 还有只海狮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.86,0:50:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海湾里好像有六条金枪鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.02,0:50:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}其中一只海狮引起了理查德的注意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.54,0:51:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}他亲昵地称这只海狮为“捉鱼小子”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.78,0:51:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只海狮很不一样 它就像是猎鱼高手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.78,0:51:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它真的很敏捷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.26,0:51:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}看着这只海狮的真实面目在镜头前呈现出来 感觉真的很有趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.62,0:51:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}无人机正在上空拍摄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.14,0:51:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这群海狮结伴猎食的画面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.06,0:51:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}我们在空中真的能看清楚这些海狮的策略{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.14,0:51:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}还能看到每只海狮扮演的角色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.98,0:51:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}捉鱼小子在水道中途就游开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.78,0:51:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它要确保金枪鱼不会逃走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.42,0:51:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}每只海狮都有自己的任务{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.50,0:51:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们真的是靠团队合作 才把金枪鱼赶到一起的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.62,0:51:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}虽然海狮一直在浅滩区猎食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.74,0:51:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过考察团队至今还没看到它们把金枪鱼赶到海滩上来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.06,0:51:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}更糟糕的是 海狮并不是这海湾里唯一的动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.34,0:51:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些直翅真鲨的身体长达两米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.02,0:52:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}鲨鱼几乎是把自己的身体拖上岸来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.38,0:52:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}然后从大海狮手里把金枪鱼偷走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.02,0:52:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}海狮现在非常生气{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.78,0:52:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}尽管有鲨鱼在场{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.22,0:52:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是为了呈现完整的故事 理直德还是需要亲自下水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.10,0:52:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}现在这是典型的鲨鱼攻击情形 浅水区里有血液{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.62,0:52:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}很容易让人认错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.14,0:52:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}小心你的手 罗比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.34,0:52:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}大家穿上了锁子甲衣服 用于护身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.58,0:52:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}这儿有很多鲨鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.90,0:52:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}一 二 三 四 五 六 一共有六头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.94,0:52:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\4a&H80&\2c&H000000&\b0}水里的血液非常多 鲨鱼们开始疯狂捕食了{\r}
